1
00:00:11,090 --> 00:00:14,850
[Fenglinwan]

2
00:00:17,160 --> 00:00:17,710
Hello.

3
00:00:18,160 --> 00:00:18,730
Hello.

4
00:00:23,920 --> 00:00:25,450
Have you seen these two men?

5
00:00:29,270 --> 00:00:30,440
They're skilled at disguises,

6
00:00:30,440 --> 00:00:33,040
so they may not look the same as
in the pictures.

7
00:00:33,280 --> 00:00:33,920
This is the suitcase

8
00:00:33,920 --> 00:00:35,560
they've been carrying around.

9
00:00:35,560 --> 00:00:37,350
If you see them,
call the police immediately.

10
00:00:37,350 --> 00:00:37,710
Okay.

11
00:00:58,220 --> 00:01:01,340
[Fenglinwan Hotel]

12
00:01:01,380 --> 00:01:09,750
[Delivery]

13
00:01:15,840 --> 00:01:16,990
They're skilled at disguises,

14
00:01:16,990 --> 00:01:19,590
so they may not look the same as
in the pictures.

15
00:01:22,150 --> 00:01:22,870
This is the suitcase

16
00:01:22,870 --> 00:01:24,020
they've been carrying around.

17
00:01:24,020 --> 00:01:26,550
If you see them,
call the police immediately.

18
00:02:48,120 --> 00:02:51,910
[Born with Luck]

19
00:02:52,020 --> 00:02:54,860
[Episode 20]

20
00:02:59,120 --> 00:03:00,280
Only the Weinan District is left.

21
00:03:00,280 --> 00:03:01,470
I'll lead the search there myself today.

22
00:03:01,470 --> 00:03:02,120
At most, one day.

23
00:03:02,120 --> 00:03:02,590
One way or another,

24
00:03:02,590 --> 00:03:04,120
we'll track those two punks down.

25
00:03:04,120 --> 00:03:05,240
T-Then, we're about to

26
00:03:05,240 --> 00:03:06,030
wrap up the case, right?

27
00:03:06,030 --> 00:03:06,760
Pretty much.

28
00:03:07,030 --> 00:03:08,230
-Chief Qi.
-Chief Qi.

29
00:03:08,430 --> 00:03:09,430
How was the meeting
at the Provincial Department?

30
00:03:09,430 --> 00:03:10,290
Very smoothly.

31
00:03:11,470 --> 00:03:13,030
How's the evidence gathering

32
00:03:13,030 --> 00:03:14,150
against Zhou Rong going?

33
00:03:14,150 --> 00:03:15,030
We've already located

34
00:03:15,030 --> 00:03:16,520
the vehicle used by the two suspects

35
00:03:16,520 --> 00:03:17,980
and have locked onto them.

36
00:03:18,360 --> 00:03:19,760
Have they been arrested?

37
00:03:20,870 --> 00:03:21,960
No, why?

38
00:03:23,310 --> 00:03:23,770
Yi'ang,

39
00:03:24,520 --> 00:03:26,520
I'm not trying to pressure you here.

40
00:03:26,630 --> 00:03:28,150
After the meeting yesterday,

41
00:03:28,150 --> 00:03:29,430
Director Gao specifically called me in

42
00:03:29,430 --> 00:03:30,079
and said

43
00:03:30,360 --> 00:03:32,960
the deadline for case review
was approaching.

44
00:03:33,470 --> 00:03:35,130
He wants a specific deadline.

45
00:03:36,030 --> 00:03:37,690
I think we need to move quickly

46
00:03:38,150 --> 00:03:39,710
and try to wrap up within the deadline.

47
00:03:39,710 --> 00:03:40,400
Within a week,

48
00:03:40,400 --> 00:03:41,000
we'll do our best to secure

49
00:03:41,000 --> 00:03:42,600
evidence against Zhou Rong.

50
00:03:42,800 --> 00:03:44,900
Given Director Gao's temperament,

51
00:03:45,430 --> 00:03:46,310
since he asked,

52
00:03:46,560 --> 00:03:48,560
he won't let us drag it out that long.

53
00:03:49,280 --> 00:03:50,680
Chief Zhang is indeed the one

54
00:03:50,680 --> 00:03:52,120
who knows Director Gao best.

55
00:03:52,120 --> 00:03:52,590
I know my mentor's temper

56
00:03:52,590 --> 00:03:53,760
too well.

57
00:03:53,960 --> 00:03:54,630
He's an impatient man,

58
00:03:54,630 --> 00:03:56,560
especially when it comes to cases.

59
00:03:56,630 --> 00:03:58,960
By noon tomorrow,
we need to have evidence in hand

60
00:03:58,960 --> 00:04:01,020
to formally open the investigation.

61
00:04:02,870 --> 00:04:03,800
And that time

62
00:04:04,590 --> 00:04:06,050
is what I fought hard for

63
00:04:06,400 --> 00:04:07,460
with Director Gao.

64
00:04:09,870 --> 00:04:10,870
Thanks, Chief Qi.

65
00:04:13,310 --> 00:04:15,110
W-What's there to thank him for?

66
00:04:18,510 --> 00:04:19,240
Chief Zhang.

67
00:04:20,240 --> 00:04:20,970
Chief Zhang.

68
00:04:24,240 --> 00:04:25,810
By tomorrow noon?

69
00:04:26,000 --> 00:04:27,310
That's way too tight.

70
00:04:31,510 --> 00:04:32,909
By Director Gao's logic,

71
00:04:33,070 --> 00:04:33,920
Zhou Rong is now

72
00:04:33,920 --> 00:04:35,240
basically like a sitting duck.

73
00:04:35,240 --> 00:04:36,310
As long as we catch those two

74
00:04:36,310 --> 00:04:37,310
and get the phone,

75
00:04:37,560 --> 00:04:39,090
we can move in and arrest Zhou Rong.

76
00:04:39,090 --> 00:04:40,490
Is it really that simple?

77
00:04:41,680 --> 00:04:42,159
Chief!

78
00:04:43,190 --> 00:04:43,680
Chief.

79
00:04:44,159 --> 00:04:45,630
Officers from the local precinct reported

80
00:04:45,630 --> 00:04:47,000
that last night,
people from Rongcheng Group

81
00:04:47,000 --> 00:04:48,190
booked tickets at Sanyang Travel Agency

82
00:04:48,190 --> 00:04:49,430
for Zhou Rong and Hu Jianren—

83
00:04:49,430 --> 00:04:50,310
a noon flight today

84
00:04:50,310 --> 00:04:52,640
from the provincial capital to Gondwana.

85
00:04:54,190 --> 00:04:55,250
Why go to Gondwana?

86
00:04:55,510 --> 00:04:56,840
They're trying to flee?

87
00:04:58,040 --> 00:04:59,159
Wang, I need you to make a trip.

88
00:04:59,159 --> 00:05:00,160
Where? Gondwana?

89
00:05:00,720 --> 00:05:01,580
To the airport.

90
00:05:01,680 --> 00:05:02,560
And play it by ear.

91
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:03,190
Without criminal evidence,

92
00:05:03,190 --> 00:05:04,790
what reason are we gonna use?

93
00:05:05,250 --> 00:05:06,310
Just play it by ear.

94
00:05:21,800 --> 00:05:22,430
Yan,

95
00:05:22,680 --> 00:05:23,740
it's Zhang Yi'ang.

96
00:05:24,040 --> 00:05:25,360
I need your help with something.

97
00:05:25,360 --> 00:05:26,560
Two people are trying to flee

98
00:05:26,560 --> 00:05:28,750
by plane from the provincial capital
at noon today.

99
00:05:28,750 --> 00:05:29,430
Can you help me

100
00:05:29,430 --> 00:05:30,360
intercept them?

101
00:05:31,480 --> 00:05:32,210
Thanks!

102
00:05:32,600 --> 00:05:33,330
I owe you one.

103
00:05:33,560 --> 00:05:34,820
Criminal suspects...

104
00:05:35,190 --> 00:05:36,400
They are suspects,

105
00:05:36,430 --> 00:05:37,040
but

106
00:05:37,270 --> 00:05:39,200
we don't have enough evidence yet.

107
00:05:39,800 --> 00:05:42,070
Aren't you familiar with border control?

108
00:05:42,070 --> 00:05:44,070
See if you can figure something out.

109
00:05:44,830 --> 00:05:46,360
How could I joke about this?

110
00:06:25,390 --> 00:06:25,920
Chief.

111
00:06:27,000 --> 00:06:29,160
The ones who robbed Zhou Rong
and beat Lang Bowen

112
00:06:29,160 --> 00:06:31,000
really weren't Mao and Xia Tinggang.

113
00:06:31,000 --> 00:06:31,930
It was these two.

114
00:06:33,000 --> 00:06:34,260
Can't see their faces.

115
00:06:34,360 --> 00:06:35,560
What should we do now?

116
00:06:38,000 --> 00:06:39,930
Let's not jump to conclusions yet.

117
00:06:40,040 --> 00:06:40,870
Try to find a way

118
00:06:40,870 --> 00:06:41,870
to get clearer photos

119
00:06:41,870 --> 00:06:42,800
of them.

120
00:06:44,850 --> 00:06:46,930
[Police]

121
00:06:50,590 --> 00:06:52,409
[Lu Zheng Car Crash Case]

122
00:06:54,950 --> 00:06:55,970
Did you bring the medicine?

123
00:06:55,970 --> 00:06:56,610
Yeah.

124
00:07:05,550 --> 00:07:06,080
Let's go!

125
00:07:14,310 --> 00:07:15,810
Thai beaches,

126
00:07:15,870 --> 00:07:16,920
Hawaiian beaches,

127
00:07:16,920 --> 00:07:18,000
Caribbean beaches—

128
00:07:18,000 --> 00:07:19,870
none of them can compare to Gondwana's.

129
00:07:19,870 --> 00:07:21,630
Gondwana has nudist beaches.

130
00:07:22,390 --> 00:07:23,270
Wonderful.

131
00:07:25,390 --> 00:07:25,950
Mr. Zhou.

132
00:07:27,040 --> 00:07:28,840
There's been a coup in Gondwana.

133
00:07:28,920 --> 00:07:29,630
What?

134
00:07:30,070 --> 00:07:31,400
The flight is canceled.

135
00:07:44,830 --> 00:07:46,490
No, why did you come over here?

136
00:07:47,190 --> 00:07:48,650
I-I'm going to make a call.

137
00:07:53,760 --> 00:07:55,220
May I... I...

138
00:07:56,190 --> 00:07:57,480
I... I...

139
00:08:00,720 --> 00:08:01,510
Excuse me?

140
00:08:02,430 --> 00:08:03,410
Yeah, it's me!

141
00:08:04,480 --> 00:08:05,680
You can call me Peter.

142
00:08:05,750 --> 00:08:06,680
I want to find...

143
00:08:06,920 --> 00:08:07,270
find...

144
00:08:07,270 --> 00:08:08,190
What's the man's name?

145
00:08:08,190 --> 00:08:09,070
Vanuatu!

146
00:08:09,120 --> 00:08:10,190
V-Vanuatu!

147
00:08:13,560 --> 00:08:14,000
What?

148
00:08:17,310 --> 00:08:18,110
Mr. Lu! Mr. Lu!

149
00:08:21,560 --> 00:08:23,070
Someone from the Municipal Bureau
just came.

150
00:08:23,070 --> 00:08:23,680
What for?

151
00:08:25,830 --> 00:08:27,390
They told us to keep an eye out
for these two people.

152
00:08:27,390 --> 00:08:28,430
And they specifically mentioned

153
00:08:28,430 --> 00:08:30,830
that those two are carrying this suitcase.

154
00:08:35,549 --> 00:08:38,840
[Never Bow to Lite]

155
00:08:40,150 --> 00:08:41,669
The Gondwana military government

156
00:08:41,669 --> 00:08:42,750
has announced that it will confiscate

157
00:08:42,750 --> 00:08:44,270
all illegal assets

158
00:08:44,320 --> 00:08:46,250
belonging to foreign colonizers.

159
00:08:46,970 --> 00:08:48,720
Do I look like a foreign colonizer?

160
00:08:48,720 --> 00:08:49,200
No.

161
00:08:49,650 --> 00:08:51,910
Then why are they confiscating my money?

162
00:08:52,120 --> 00:08:53,790
And "Never Bow to Lite?"

163
00:08:53,790 --> 00:08:55,010
What the hell does that even mean?

164
00:08:54,150 --> 00:08:55,510
[Never Bow to Lite]

165
00:08:55,230 --> 00:08:55,760
Mr. Zhou,

166
00:08:56,120 --> 00:08:56,730
I think...

167
00:09:02,400 --> 00:09:02,930
Hello?

168
00:09:12,030 --> 00:09:12,830
There's hope.

169
00:09:12,870 --> 00:09:13,790
Lu Yibo called.

170
00:09:17,080 --> 00:09:18,440
He said the police are
looking for two people

171
00:09:18,440 --> 00:09:19,970
carrying a black suitcase.

172
00:09:21,080 --> 00:09:23,030
Based on the photos the police provided,

173
00:09:23,030 --> 00:09:25,110
those two are not the ones who robbed you.

174
00:09:25,110 --> 00:09:25,880
So the police

175
00:09:25,910 --> 00:09:27,080
can't possibly get the phone

176
00:09:27,080 --> 00:09:27,960
from them.

177
00:09:30,720 --> 00:09:32,250
Let's stay in Sanjiangkou.

178
00:09:32,720 --> 00:09:35,380
We might still have a chance
to turn this around.

179
00:09:35,960 --> 00:09:37,160
Turn around, my foot.

180
00:09:40,070 --> 00:09:41,160
That one seems to be

181
00:09:41,910 --> 00:09:43,360
"Never Bow to Life."

182
00:09:45,190 --> 00:09:46,220
Isn't it "Lite"?

183
00:09:47,480 --> 00:09:48,280
Close enough.

184
00:09:53,860 --> 00:09:54,360
Go back.

185
00:09:55,390 --> 00:09:56,790
And track down those jerks

186
00:09:56,790 --> 00:09:57,920
who screwed me over.

187
00:10:01,670 --> 00:10:02,080
Chief.

188
00:10:17,240 --> 00:10:17,850
Chief.

189
00:10:19,030 --> 00:10:19,550
The HD photos

190
00:10:19,550 --> 00:10:20,640
of those two are in.

191
00:10:20,790 --> 00:10:22,920
It was indeed not Mao and Xia Tinggang.

192
00:10:24,600 --> 00:10:26,060
Should I notify everyone?

193
00:10:28,140 --> 00:10:30,320
[Lu Yibo] [Report Zhou Rong]

194
00:10:28,320 --> 00:10:29,580
Bring Lu Yibo in first.

195
00:10:31,770 --> 00:10:32,260
Okay.

196
00:10:39,000 --> 00:10:39,730
Chief Zhang.

197
00:10:42,090 --> 00:10:43,630
Zhou Rong didn't manage to leave.

198
00:10:43,630 --> 00:10:45,030
He went back to his villa.

199
00:10:45,200 --> 00:10:45,600
Good!

200
00:10:46,550 --> 00:10:47,150
Good!

201
00:10:49,510 --> 00:10:50,080
Good!

202
00:10:54,200 --> 00:10:55,660
Justice won't let him go.

203
00:10:55,790 --> 00:10:56,240
Good.

204
00:10:56,440 --> 00:10:56,870
-Yeah.
-Yeah.

205
00:10:56,870 --> 00:10:57,270
Yeah.

206
00:10:58,630 --> 00:10:59,000
Good.

207
00:10:59,390 --> 00:10:59,750
Good.

208
00:11:01,550 --> 00:11:03,010
I'll go report to Chief Qi.

209
00:11:03,600 --> 00:11:04,900
Zhou Rong's not getting away.

210
00:11:04,900 --> 00:11:05,910
Absolutely not!

211
00:11:05,910 --> 00:11:07,440
He can't get away this time.

212
00:11:13,080 --> 00:11:14,410
He's done for this time.

213
00:11:17,120 --> 00:11:18,030
Zhou Rong didn't leave?

214
00:11:18,030 --> 00:11:18,890
What happened?

215
00:11:22,240 --> 00:11:23,170
What's that for?

216
00:11:24,790 --> 00:11:25,870
Drop the act.

217
00:11:26,910 --> 00:11:27,750
What are you talking about?

218
00:11:27,750 --> 00:11:28,680
The two-man con.

219
00:11:29,480 --> 00:11:30,600
What two-man con?

220
00:11:31,550 --> 00:11:32,350
Are you crazy?

221
00:11:39,150 --> 00:11:39,960
I know

222
00:11:40,000 --> 00:11:40,930
everything now.

223
00:11:41,870 --> 00:11:42,910
The Chief knew all along

224
00:11:42,910 --> 00:11:44,080
that Mao and Xia Tinggang

225
00:11:44,080 --> 00:11:46,000
weren't the ones who robbed Zhou Rong.

226
00:11:46,000 --> 00:11:46,720
Pursuing them was just

227
00:11:46,720 --> 00:11:49,050
a smokescreen to keep Zhou Rong off guard.

228
00:11:50,320 --> 00:11:51,720
Why did the Chief do that?

229
00:11:53,320 --> 00:11:54,450
If you were Zhou Rong

230
00:11:54,840 --> 00:11:56,750
and the most damning evidence against you
went missing

231
00:11:56,750 --> 00:11:58,030
while the police were searching for it,

232
00:11:58,030 --> 00:11:59,030
what would you do?

233
00:12:00,220 --> 00:12:01,720
Find it before the police do.

234
00:12:01,720 --> 00:12:02,120
Wrong.

235
00:12:03,150 --> 00:12:04,240
The safer move

236
00:12:04,270 --> 00:12:05,510
would be to run immediately.

237
00:12:05,510 --> 00:12:07,240
Just like Zhou Rong tried to do.

238
00:12:08,600 --> 00:12:09,870
Yesterday, when you said

239
00:12:09,870 --> 00:12:12,360
Mao and Xia Tinggang
weren't the real culprits,

240
00:12:12,360 --> 00:12:14,360
the Chief had already believed you.

241
00:12:14,720 --> 00:12:16,360
But why did he still ask us to distribute

242
00:12:16,360 --> 00:12:17,820
their photos everywhere?

243
00:12:17,850 --> 00:12:19,780
To keep Zhou Rong calm and in place.

244
00:12:22,150 --> 00:12:23,630
But how would Zhou Rong see

245
00:12:23,670 --> 00:12:25,000
the photos we distributed?

246
00:12:25,000 --> 00:12:26,860
I just came back from Fenglinwan.

247
00:12:26,960 --> 00:12:28,550
The Chief specifically emphasized

248
00:12:28,550 --> 00:12:30,360
distributing them
to hotels and restaurants.

249
00:12:30,360 --> 00:12:31,200
Would punks

250
00:12:31,240 --> 00:12:32,240
like Mao and Xia Tinggang

251
00:12:32,240 --> 00:12:33,770
ever go to places like that?

252
00:12:33,840 --> 00:12:34,840
Still denying it?

253
00:12:37,500 --> 00:12:38,360
Then how did you figure out

254
00:12:38,360 --> 00:12:39,360
the Chief's plan?

255
00:12:40,750 --> 00:12:42,460
Don't think you're the only smart ones—

256
00:12:42,460 --> 00:12:43,960
keeping everything from me like that.

257
00:12:43,960 --> 00:12:44,960
But I'm diligent.

258
00:12:46,120 --> 00:12:48,180
Yesterday, the Chief recited a poem:

259
00:12:48,200 --> 00:12:49,120
"Sorrowful eyes,

260
00:12:49,120 --> 00:12:50,910
unable to see through your heart."

261
00:12:50,910 --> 00:12:51,670
That's from a piece he published

262
00:12:51,670 --> 00:12:53,910
in the Provincial Department's
monthly journal four years ago.

263
00:12:53,910 --> 00:12:54,630
The title is

264
00:12:54,720 --> 00:12:56,320
"I Won't Let You Leave."

265
00:12:56,750 --> 00:12:57,750
Who didn't leave?

266
00:12:57,960 --> 00:12:59,290
Zhou Rong didn't leave.

267
00:12:59,790 --> 00:13:00,750
I've carefully read every poem

268
00:13:00,750 --> 00:13:02,280
the Chief has ever written.

269
00:13:05,240 --> 00:13:06,500
Hello, the task force.

270
00:13:08,600 --> 00:13:09,080
Really?

271
00:13:09,550 --> 00:13:10,750
How did you find them?

272
00:13:11,550 --> 00:13:11,910
Okay.

273
00:13:12,280 --> 00:13:13,140
What happened?

274
00:13:14,000 --> 00:13:15,270
They found the two real suspects

275
00:13:15,270 --> 00:13:16,730
at Ruihao Boutique Hotel.

276
00:13:17,320 --> 00:13:18,390
Are you sure it's them?

277
00:13:18,390 --> 00:13:19,840
We haven't even sent out the photos yet.

278
00:13:19,840 --> 00:13:20,720
It was a delivery worker

279
00:13:20,720 --> 00:13:22,380
who recognized the suitcase.

280
00:13:23,150 --> 00:13:23,950
See?

281
00:13:24,320 --> 00:13:25,240
It was also the Chief's idea

282
00:13:25,240 --> 00:13:27,440
to send out the photos of that suitcase.

283
00:13:28,550 --> 00:13:30,240
Li Qian and Song Xing
are already on their way.

284
00:13:30,240 --> 00:13:31,150
Tell them not to go in yet

285
00:13:31,150 --> 00:13:32,080
and wait until we get there.

286
00:13:32,080 --> 00:13:32,600
Okay.

287
00:13:37,660 --> 00:13:39,660
[Loyalty]

288
00:13:46,970 --> 00:13:47,480
Stop, stop.

289
00:13:47,480 --> 00:13:48,210
Chief Zhang.

290
00:13:51,130 --> 00:13:52,330
Let him go in and wait!

291
00:14:03,060 --> 00:14:06,320
[Ruihao Boutique Hotel]

292
00:14:12,240 --> 00:14:14,240
How about I go in
and scope out the situation first?

293
00:14:14,240 --> 00:14:16,440
Let's wait for the Chief and the others.

294
00:14:16,510 --> 00:14:17,710
What if it's not them?

295
00:14:18,720 --> 00:14:20,320
You stay here and keep watch.

296
00:14:21,340 --> 00:14:27,560
[Ruihao Boutique Hotel]

297
00:14:34,840 --> 00:14:35,370
Hello.

298
00:14:38,750 --> 00:14:39,470
What?

299
00:14:42,670 --> 00:14:43,080
[Police]

300
00:14:44,250 --> 00:14:45,380
Officer?

301
00:14:45,840 --> 00:14:46,870
What's the matter?

302
00:14:46,870 --> 00:14:48,800
Let me see the surveillance video.

303
00:14:52,670 --> 00:14:53,530
What happened?

304
00:14:54,150 --> 00:14:54,670
Well...

305
00:15:05,080 --> 00:15:05,630
Chao,

306
00:15:06,270 --> 00:15:08,530
I don't want to pretend to be blind today.

307
00:15:09,130 --> 00:15:11,060
I also wanted to give you a new look.

308
00:15:11,200 --> 00:15:12,530
But do we have anything?

309
00:15:12,630 --> 00:15:16,160
Would we be in this mess
if you hadn't caused trouble yesterday?

310
00:15:17,440 --> 00:15:18,000
Chao.

311
00:15:19,750 --> 00:15:22,320
I think you're better at
acting blind than I am.

312
00:15:22,320 --> 00:15:23,980
Today you'll be the blind one.

313
00:15:58,000 --> 00:16:00,050
I just want to get a room
with my girlfriend.

314
00:16:00,050 --> 00:16:01,450
Can we do it without an ID?

315
00:16:01,540 --> 00:16:02,510
No problem.

316
00:16:06,240 --> 00:16:08,970
Honey, did you bring
my disability certificate?

317
00:16:09,080 --> 00:16:11,410
Did you bring my disability certificate?

318
00:16:11,510 --> 00:16:12,080
No.

319
00:16:12,080 --> 00:16:13,720
Let's go back and get it.

320
00:16:31,750 --> 00:16:32,880
What's wrong, Chao?

321
00:16:33,200 --> 00:16:34,530
I think that guy's a cop.

322
00:16:35,200 --> 00:16:36,130
What do you want?

323
00:16:37,600 --> 00:16:38,360
We go all in.

324
00:16:44,870 --> 00:16:45,490
[Shiweixuan Restaurant]

325
00:16:47,550 --> 00:16:48,120
All in.

326
00:17:07,920 --> 00:17:08,319
Hello?

327
00:17:08,550 --> 00:17:08,960
Hello?

328
00:17:09,200 --> 00:17:09,920
I've trapped the suspects

329
00:17:09,920 --> 00:17:10,640
in the room.

330
00:17:10,829 --> 00:17:11,400
Requesting backup.

331
00:17:11,400 --> 00:17:12,680
Chao, this pillow is too small.

332
00:17:12,680 --> 00:17:13,589
I'm afraid we'll sprain our ankles.

333
00:17:13,589 --> 00:17:14,170
Idiot,

334
00:17:14,200 --> 00:17:15,000
when jumping from a height,

335
00:17:15,000 --> 00:17:17,730
the most important thing
is to protect your head.

336
00:17:26,400 --> 00:17:26,880
I...

337
00:17:42,240 --> 00:17:43,880
Hurry! They ran away!

338
00:17:48,350 --> 00:17:49,540
Where is the back door?

339
00:17:49,540 --> 00:17:50,800
Where is the back door?

340
00:17:54,510 --> 00:17:55,090
Chao,

341
00:17:55,200 --> 00:17:56,640
why are we taking the back door?

342
00:17:56,640 --> 00:17:58,350
There must be an ambush at the front door.

343
00:17:58,350 --> 00:17:59,280
Freeze! Police!

344
00:18:02,390 --> 00:18:04,060
You brat, you can still sit up?

345
00:18:04,090 --> 00:18:04,730
Let's go!

346
00:18:06,180 --> 00:18:07,110
Freeze! Police!

347
00:18:09,000 --> 00:18:09,630
Are you okay?

348
00:18:09,630 --> 00:18:11,230
Never mind me, go after them!

349
00:18:12,270 --> 00:18:12,930
Suspects spotted.

350
00:18:12,850 --> 00:18:14,130
♪ He ♪

351
00:18:12,960 --> 00:18:14,090
Requesting backup!

352
00:18:15,600 --> 00:18:19,840
♪ A rusted flower etched
across his chest ♪

353
00:18:21,890 --> 00:18:22,860
♪ Oh, he ♪

354
00:18:24,690 --> 00:18:27,980
♪ Says your worldview's still too small ♪

355
00:18:31,820 --> 00:18:35,670
♪ A rat that steals rice—
humans call it cunning ♪

356
00:18:36,320 --> 00:18:40,230
♪ A human who steals honey—
calls the bees hardworking ♪

357
00:18:40,890 --> 00:18:44,840
♪ Absurd, greedy—
self-proclaimed superior beings ♪

358
00:18:45,410 --> 00:18:48,060
♪ Hypocritical, wasteful, hollow ♪

359
00:18:47,160 --> 00:18:47,620
Freeze!

360
00:18:54,640 --> 00:18:55,200
Stop!

361
00:19:15,700 --> 00:19:17,450
[Professional Bicycle Repair]

362
00:19:31,720 --> 00:19:32,250
This way.

363
00:19:41,110 --> 00:19:41,960
When we were coming this way,

364
00:19:41,960 --> 00:19:43,150
we didn't know what was going on.

365
00:19:43,150 --> 00:19:44,310
Boom! It just exploded.

366
00:19:44,310 --> 00:19:46,040
Yeah, scared the hell out of me.

367
00:19:46,830 --> 00:19:48,590
This is so gross!

368
00:19:48,620 --> 00:19:49,080
Well...

369
00:19:49,200 --> 00:19:50,310
It's everywhere!

370
00:19:51,000 --> 00:19:51,980
How are we supposed to get through?

371
00:19:51,980 --> 00:19:52,800
It stinks!

372
00:19:53,920 --> 00:19:55,380
Why didn't you wait for us?

373
00:19:55,550 --> 00:19:57,010
Why did you act on your own?

374
00:19:57,030 --> 00:19:58,260
I didn't act on my own.

375
00:19:58,350 --> 00:19:59,680
I just wanted to go in and confirm

376
00:19:59,680 --> 00:20:01,190
whether it was really those two.

377
00:20:01,190 --> 00:20:02,310
I didn't even give away my identity.

378
00:20:02,310 --> 00:20:02,830
I don't know why,

379
00:20:02,830 --> 00:20:03,440
but they just ran away.

380
00:20:03,440 --> 00:20:03,920
Song Xing,

381
00:20:03,920 --> 00:20:05,440
this isn't the first time
you've screwed up.

382
00:20:05,440 --> 00:20:06,240
What exactly do you want?

383
00:20:06,240 --> 00:20:07,240
Had enough of being
a criminal police officer?

384
00:20:07,240 --> 00:20:08,030
Want to go push papers
at the Household Registration Office,

385
00:20:08,030 --> 00:20:08,480
huh?

386
00:20:09,880 --> 00:20:10,750
Go to the hospital first.

387
00:20:10,750 --> 00:20:11,920
Chief, I'm actually fine.

388
00:20:11,920 --> 00:20:12,400
Stop arguing!

389
00:20:12,400 --> 00:20:13,460
Go to the hospital!

390
00:20:24,510 --> 00:20:24,960
Chief Zhang.

391
00:20:24,960 --> 00:20:25,760
Captain Wang.

392
00:20:26,350 --> 00:20:28,070
The way those two blew up the sewer

393
00:20:28,070 --> 00:20:29,000
is identical to

394
00:20:29,000 --> 00:20:31,260
the provincial capital explosion case.

395
00:20:32,030 --> 00:20:32,750
Let's go to the hotel first,

396
00:20:32,750 --> 00:20:34,310
collect biological evidence of those two,

397
00:20:34,310 --> 00:20:34,910
and take it

398
00:20:34,920 --> 00:20:35,790
to compare with the one

399
00:20:35,790 --> 00:20:36,750
from the explosion case.

400
00:20:36,750 --> 00:20:37,280
Yes, sir.

401
00:20:39,270 --> 00:20:40,000
Chief Zhang.

402
00:20:40,830 --> 00:20:42,080
It's already noon.

403
00:20:42,310 --> 00:20:43,350
Can we still make it

404
00:20:43,350 --> 00:20:44,480
by tomorrow at noon?

405
00:20:45,400 --> 00:20:46,070
Can't we?

406
00:20:46,550 --> 00:20:47,110
Can't we?

407
00:20:51,000 --> 00:20:51,640
Can we?

408
00:20:53,310 --> 00:20:54,260
Right now,

409
00:20:54,300 --> 00:20:55,920
these are the people involved:

410
00:20:55,920 --> 00:20:56,400
me,

411
00:20:57,720 --> 00:20:58,200
you,

412
00:20:58,990 --> 00:20:59,690
Zhu Yifei,

413
00:21:00,400 --> 00:21:01,060
Lang Bowen,

414
00:21:02,350 --> 00:21:03,010
and Lu Yibo.

415
00:21:03,640 --> 00:21:05,200
Lang Bowen is the most suspicious.

416
00:21:05,200 --> 00:21:06,350
But even if he wanted to drag me down—

417
00:21:06,350 --> 00:21:07,720
he took care of Lu Zheng himself.

418
00:21:07,720 --> 00:21:08,510
There's no way he'd just sit in a hospital

419
00:21:08,510 --> 00:21:09,710
waiting to be caught.

420
00:21:09,820 --> 00:21:10,750
As for Zhu Yifei,

421
00:21:11,030 --> 00:21:12,460
he's an outsider.

422
00:21:12,550 --> 00:21:13,380
He has neither the motive

423
00:21:13,380 --> 00:21:15,240
nor the influence to mess with me.

424
00:21:19,720 --> 00:21:20,250
Mr. Zhou.

425
00:21:21,240 --> 00:21:22,640
Whoever I might suspect,

426
00:21:22,920 --> 00:21:24,030
it wouldn't be you.

427
00:21:26,240 --> 00:21:27,720
Mr. Zhou, Ren!

428
00:21:28,270 --> 00:21:28,940
Um...

429
00:21:29,550 --> 00:21:30,270
This morning,

430
00:21:30,270 --> 00:21:32,170
Lu Yibo went to
the Municipal Public Security Bureau.

431
00:21:32,170 --> 00:21:33,350
What did he go there for?

432
00:21:33,350 --> 00:21:33,830
No idea.

433
00:21:34,480 --> 00:21:35,440
But the people at Fenglinwan said

434
00:21:35,440 --> 00:21:36,570
he definitely went.

435
00:21:43,790 --> 00:21:45,670
I've underestimated you.

436
00:21:47,080 --> 00:21:47,790
You go right now

437
00:21:47,790 --> 00:21:49,160
and wait outside the Municipal Bureau.

438
00:21:49,160 --> 00:21:50,070
As soon as he comes out,

439
00:21:50,070 --> 00:21:51,560
bring him here!

440
00:21:52,370 --> 00:21:54,050
[Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau]

441
00:22:12,030 --> 00:22:12,590
Officer,

442
00:22:13,350 --> 00:22:14,200
when will Chief Zhang

443
00:22:14,200 --> 00:22:15,310
be able to receive me?

444
00:22:15,310 --> 00:22:15,970
"Receive?"

445
00:22:17,030 --> 00:22:18,640
No, question me.

446
00:22:18,720 --> 00:22:19,450
"Question?"

447
00:22:20,680 --> 00:22:22,240
What's the proper term then?

448
00:22:22,240 --> 00:22:23,000
I can't just wait here

449
00:22:23,000 --> 00:22:23,930
forever, right?

450
00:22:24,350 --> 00:22:26,000
The Chief went out on official business.

451
00:22:26,000 --> 00:22:27,790
Just wait patiently as you were told.

452
00:22:27,790 --> 00:22:28,240
If you don't want to wait,

453
00:22:28,240 --> 00:22:29,570
you can leave right now.

454
00:22:48,830 --> 00:22:49,310
Chief.

455
00:22:52,830 --> 00:22:53,840
Life is

456
00:22:54,030 --> 00:22:55,230
full of ups and downs.

457
00:23:00,830 --> 00:23:02,550
You have to endure the quiet times

458
00:23:02,550 --> 00:23:04,410
before you can embrace the glory.

459
00:23:06,030 --> 00:23:06,720
Am I really going to be

460
00:23:06,720 --> 00:23:08,200
transferred away from the frontline?

461
00:23:08,200 --> 00:23:09,240
Who said that? No.

462
00:23:10,160 --> 00:23:10,720
Then why are you

463
00:23:10,720 --> 00:23:11,920
saying all that to me?

464
00:23:12,920 --> 00:23:14,210
I just think...

465
00:23:14,270 --> 00:23:15,870
You don't need to comfort me.

466
00:23:16,110 --> 00:23:18,080
Just tell me the truth.

467
00:23:18,200 --> 00:23:18,880
Am I really being

468
00:23:18,880 --> 00:23:20,270
transferred to
the Household Registration Office?

469
00:23:20,270 --> 00:23:21,270
You can't go there.

470
00:23:21,270 --> 00:23:23,270
Their staffing quota is already full.

471
00:23:23,270 --> 00:23:24,470
Then where am I going?

472
00:23:24,680 --> 00:23:25,480
Nowhere.

473
00:23:26,310 --> 00:23:27,880
You're staying with the task force.

474
00:23:27,880 --> 00:23:29,680
Why aren't you disciplining me?

475
00:23:30,790 --> 00:23:32,190
Think about it yourself.

476
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:39,090
Unless I didn't do anything wrong.

477
00:23:39,280 --> 00:23:40,340
Is that it, Chief?

478
00:23:41,590 --> 00:23:43,390
You could interpret it that way.

479
00:23:50,400 --> 00:23:51,400
I understand now.

480
00:23:53,270 --> 00:23:54,000
Chief Zhang!

481
00:23:55,240 --> 00:23:56,040
Captain Wang!

482
00:23:58,030 --> 00:24:00,690
You're like
a completely different person now.

483
00:24:01,480 --> 00:24:02,930
What did the Chief say to you?

484
00:24:02,930 --> 00:24:03,650
The Chief

485
00:24:03,680 --> 00:24:04,810
told me everything.

486
00:24:05,160 --> 00:24:05,680
Understood?

487
00:24:05,680 --> 00:24:06,410
Understood.

488
00:24:06,680 --> 00:24:08,590
Understand the Chief's intentions now?

489
00:24:08,590 --> 00:24:09,030
I do.

490
00:24:10,000 --> 00:24:11,600
No more mistakes from now on.

491
00:24:11,880 --> 00:24:12,410
Yes, sir.

492
00:24:13,640 --> 00:24:14,370
Chief Zhang.

493
00:24:15,270 --> 00:24:17,000
The fingerprint match results

494
00:24:17,160 --> 00:24:19,160
for Liu Bei's killer have come back.

495
00:24:19,960 --> 00:24:20,350
Huo Zheng.

496
00:24:20,080 --> 00:24:22,180
[Wanted Person Registration Form]

497
00:24:20,720 --> 00:24:21,440
He's also a hitman,

498
00:24:21,440 --> 00:24:22,240
a wanted criminal.

499
00:24:22,240 --> 00:24:24,170
He was there to protect the seller.

500
00:24:25,830 --> 00:24:26,500
Find him.

501
00:24:27,960 --> 00:24:29,480
Why are you still standing here?
Go issue the wanted notice.

502
00:24:29,480 --> 00:24:30,010
Yes, sir!

503
00:24:32,750 --> 00:24:33,610
One more thing.

504
00:24:33,830 --> 00:24:35,630
Lu Yibo is still waiting for you.

505
00:24:35,880 --> 00:24:37,010
He's still waiting?

506
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:38,060
Let him go back.

507
00:24:38,980 --> 00:24:40,580
He's been waiting here all day,
and you're not going to see him?

508
00:24:40,580 --> 00:24:41,270
Well,

509
00:24:41,590 --> 00:24:42,850
we almost caught the suspects today.

510
00:24:42,850 --> 00:24:43,390
What

511
00:24:43,590 --> 00:24:45,000
could we possibly
get out of him at this point?

512
00:24:45,000 --> 00:24:46,160
Let's focus on the important work.

513
00:24:46,160 --> 00:24:46,960
Send him home. Let him go.

514
00:24:46,960 --> 00:24:47,490
Alright.

515
00:24:49,400 --> 00:24:50,030
Doctor.

516
00:24:51,030 --> 00:24:52,960
Doctor, could you
take a look at this for me?

517
00:24:52,960 --> 00:24:53,690
I'm off duty.

518
00:24:53,830 --> 00:24:54,960
Come back at 1:00 PM.

519
00:24:55,160 --> 00:24:55,750
Sorry,

520
00:24:55,790 --> 00:24:57,750
but could you just take a quick look?

521
00:24:57,750 --> 00:24:58,520
Lately,

522
00:24:58,550 --> 00:24:59,680
I've had no appetite

523
00:24:59,720 --> 00:25:01,250
and constantly feel tired.

524
00:24:59,800 --> 00:25:00,670
[Sanjiangkou People's Hospital
Laboratory Test Report]

525
00:25:00,710 --> 00:25:02,030
[Test Item] [Sex Hormone Panel]

526
00:25:01,400 --> 00:25:01,960
I want to know

527
00:25:01,960 --> 00:25:03,820
if I have an endocrine imbalance.

528
00:25:05,110 --> 00:25:06,770
Based on your hormone levels,

529
00:25:06,920 --> 00:25:07,920
you're pregnant.

530
00:25:09,480 --> 00:25:10,610
That's impossible.

531
00:25:10,750 --> 00:25:11,680
Nothing has happened.

532
00:25:11,680 --> 00:25:12,510
Nothing what?

533
00:25:14,920 --> 00:25:16,320
It's only been a few days.

534
00:25:16,440 --> 00:25:17,070
Go get

535
00:25:17,070 --> 00:25:18,400
a beta-hCG test.

536
00:25:18,550 --> 00:25:19,880
Even if it's just a week into pregnancy,

537
00:25:19,880 --> 00:25:21,620
the test can pick it up.

538
00:25:22,310 --> 00:25:23,240
Thank you.

539
00:25:25,650 --> 00:25:27,420
[Test Item] [Sex Hormone Panel]

540
00:25:28,640 --> 00:25:29,590
I'm pregnant?

541
00:25:48,680 --> 00:25:49,440
Get in.

542
00:26:08,640 --> 00:26:09,240
Ren.

543
00:26:10,750 --> 00:26:11,830
Where are we going?

544
00:26:13,790 --> 00:26:15,190
Mr. Rong wants to see you.

545
00:26:16,000 --> 00:26:16,930
What's it about?

546
00:26:31,240 --> 00:26:31,790
Hello?

547
00:26:32,350 --> 00:26:33,200
Hello, Yibo.

548
00:26:33,880 --> 00:26:35,550
I have good news for you.

549
00:26:37,310 --> 00:26:38,840
You're going to be a father!

550
00:26:42,970 --> 00:26:44,430
Let's talk when I get back.

551
00:26:45,070 --> 00:26:45,870
What's wrong?

552
00:26:46,750 --> 00:26:47,550
Where are you?

553
00:26:49,480 --> 00:26:50,740
I'm in Ren's car.

554
00:26:51,160 --> 00:26:52,670
Where are you going with Ren?

555
00:26:52,670 --> 00:26:54,470
Mr. Zhou needs me for something.

556
00:26:54,590 --> 00:26:56,050
Why does he want to see you?

557
00:26:56,180 --> 00:26:56,910
Stop asking.

558
00:26:57,190 --> 00:26:57,850
I have to go.

559
00:27:16,000 --> 00:27:17,190
So, what did you

560
00:27:17,720 --> 00:27:19,350
talk about with Zhang Yi'ang?

561
00:27:19,350 --> 00:27:19,790
Rong,

562
00:27:20,330 --> 00:27:21,990
I really didn't get to see him.

563
00:27:22,350 --> 00:27:23,770
Then who did you see?

564
00:27:24,070 --> 00:27:25,200
I didn't see anyone.

565
00:27:26,240 --> 00:27:27,610
They just had me waiting

566
00:27:27,640 --> 00:27:29,270
i-in a meeting room the whole time,

567
00:27:29,270 --> 00:27:31,400
a-and then let me go.

568
00:27:33,070 --> 00:27:34,930
The world shouldn't be like this.

569
00:27:35,680 --> 00:27:36,540
People

570
00:27:37,200 --> 00:27:38,930
shouldn't be like this either.

571
00:27:40,160 --> 00:27:40,690
Mr. Zhou,

572
00:27:41,400 --> 00:27:42,520
if I'm lying to you,

573
00:27:42,960 --> 00:27:44,510
I can die right now!

574
00:27:45,960 --> 00:27:46,750
How?

575
00:27:48,440 --> 00:27:49,440
Could you bear to?

576
00:27:53,270 --> 00:27:53,830
What?

577
00:27:54,720 --> 00:27:56,880
Getting desperate enough
to do something rash?

578
00:27:56,880 --> 00:27:57,310
Rong,

579
00:27:58,030 --> 00:27:59,000
if you don't believe me,

580
00:27:59,000 --> 00:27:59,640
I'll jump now

581
00:27:59,640 --> 00:28:00,680
and drown myself!

582
00:28:02,070 --> 00:28:02,880
If you don't let me up,

583
00:28:02,880 --> 00:28:04,480
I won't take a single breath!

584
00:28:12,640 --> 00:28:13,270
Yibo!

585
00:28:13,640 --> 00:28:14,310
Yibo!

586
00:28:16,030 --> 00:28:17,560
You're serious about this?

587
00:28:18,310 --> 00:28:19,790
Come up here and explain yourself clearly.

588
00:28:19,790 --> 00:28:21,440
No need to be so drastic about it!

589
00:28:21,440 --> 00:28:22,550
He can't hear you.

590
00:28:22,920 --> 00:28:24,030
I have experience.

591
00:28:25,440 --> 00:28:26,440
When I had an episode last time,

592
00:28:26,440 --> 00:28:27,400
you were shouting outside,
and I couldn't hear a thing,

593
00:28:27,400 --> 00:28:28,460
no matter how loud.

594
00:28:30,400 --> 00:28:33,060
How long did I stay underwater
in that fish tank?

595
00:28:33,790 --> 00:28:35,110
Two or three minutes.

596
00:28:37,110 --> 00:28:38,170
If he's still alive

597
00:28:38,750 --> 00:28:39,950
after three minutes,

598
00:28:40,830 --> 00:28:41,560
pull him out.

599
00:28:42,550 --> 00:28:43,830
What if he can't hold it

600
00:28:43,920 --> 00:28:44,980
and comes up early?

601
00:28:51,810 --> 00:28:52,720
What comes after

602
00:28:52,720 --> 00:28:53,960
is yours to handle.

603
00:28:55,110 --> 00:28:56,860
We grew up together.

604
00:28:57,310 --> 00:28:58,910
I can't bring myself to do it.

605
00:28:59,240 --> 00:28:59,970
Understood.

606
00:29:02,240 --> 00:29:04,950
[Alarm] [3:00 minutes]

607
00:29:04,640 --> 00:29:05,170
Mr. Zhou!

608
00:29:05,480 --> 00:29:06,000
Ren!

609
00:29:06,880 --> 00:29:07,420
Um,

610
00:29:07,640 --> 00:29:08,500
Zhou Qi is here.

611
00:29:08,960 --> 00:29:09,850
Mr. Zhou!

612
00:29:10,920 --> 00:29:11,480
Mr. Zhou.

613
00:29:12,350 --> 00:29:13,150
Where is Yibo?

614
00:29:13,720 --> 00:29:14,520
Yibo...

615
00:29:14,640 --> 00:29:15,400
is swimming.

616
00:29:17,030 --> 00:29:17,640
Yibo!

617
00:29:18,790 --> 00:29:19,470
Mr. Zhou.

618
00:29:19,550 --> 00:29:20,250
Mr. Zhou.

619
00:29:20,310 --> 00:29:21,240
I'm begging you.

620
00:29:21,830 --> 00:29:23,100
Please let him go.

621
00:29:23,590 --> 00:29:24,970
Please spare him.

622
00:29:25,720 --> 00:29:26,400
Qi,

623
00:29:27,550 --> 00:29:28,800
Yibo is playing a game

624
00:29:28,830 --> 00:29:30,110
with Mr. Zhou.

625
00:29:31,550 --> 00:29:32,310
He's doing it willingly.

626
00:29:32,310 --> 00:29:33,440
No one's forcing him.

627
00:29:33,440 --> 00:29:34,110
Yibo!

628
00:29:34,720 --> 00:29:35,640
Yibo!

629
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:37,910
If we die, we die together.

630
00:29:38,000 --> 00:29:39,680
The three of us die together!

631
00:29:39,830 --> 00:29:40,480
Yibo,

632
00:29:40,590 --> 00:29:41,550
I'm coming!

633
00:29:43,350 --> 00:29:44,160
Yibo!

634
00:29:44,960 --> 00:29:45,720
Yibo!

635
00:29:46,910 --> 00:29:49,040
-What a couple those two are...
-Yibo!

636
00:29:49,240 --> 00:29:51,530
She just said "the three of us."

637
00:29:51,790 --> 00:29:52,720
Who's the third?

638
00:29:55,030 --> 00:29:56,400
What are you doing?

639
00:29:56,400 --> 00:29:57,090
Qi,

640
00:29:57,200 --> 00:29:58,380
why are you here?

641
00:29:58,440 --> 00:29:59,960
I was worried about you!

642
00:29:59,960 --> 00:30:00,640
Mr. Zhou,

643
00:30:01,310 --> 00:30:02,750
two minutes, fifty-nine seconds.

644
00:30:02,750 --> 00:30:03,420
Mr. Zhou,

645
00:30:03,790 --> 00:30:04,960
she didn't know anything

646
00:30:04,960 --> 00:30:06,510
about me coming to the police station!

647
00:30:06,510 --> 00:30:07,120
Mr. Zhou,

648
00:30:07,140 --> 00:30:08,270
should we fulfill their wish?

649
00:30:08,270 --> 00:30:09,580
No, no, no!

650
00:30:10,440 --> 00:30:11,870
I'll go back to drowning.

651
00:30:12,070 --> 00:30:12,720
Please,

652
00:30:13,070 --> 00:30:14,510
let her go, okay?

653
00:30:15,480 --> 00:30:15,960
I'm pregnant.

654
00:30:15,960 --> 00:30:17,640
She's carrying my child.

655
00:30:20,160 --> 00:30:21,310
W-Who...

656
00:30:21,750 --> 00:30:22,810
W-Who is pregnant?

657
00:30:23,000 --> 00:30:24,240
What kind of question is that?

658
00:30:24,240 --> 00:30:24,880
He said she's pregnant.

659
00:30:24,880 --> 00:30:25,750
She's the only woman here.

660
00:30:25,750 --> 00:30:26,750
Who else could it be?

661
00:30:26,750 --> 00:30:27,750
No, he...

662
00:30:28,000 --> 00:30:29,270
How would I know?

663
00:30:29,510 --> 00:30:29,960
Rong.

664
00:30:31,270 --> 00:30:32,030
Mr. Zhou.

665
00:30:35,630 --> 00:30:36,440
Mr. Zhou.

666
00:30:37,030 --> 00:30:39,360
Please, let my child
have a chance to live.

667
00:30:41,550 --> 00:30:42,270
Mr. Zhou,

668
00:30:42,640 --> 00:30:44,020
I'm begging you.

669
00:30:44,350 --> 00:30:45,510
Please let us go.

670
00:30:45,590 --> 00:30:47,850
Our child can't grow up without a father.

671
00:30:48,920 --> 00:30:49,440
I...

672
00:30:50,000 --> 00:30:50,740
Lu Yibo, I...

673
00:30:50,770 --> 00:30:52,510
Which word of yours
am I supposed to believe?

674
00:30:52,510 --> 00:30:54,040
You told me you couldn't...

675
00:30:55,750 --> 00:30:57,720
You told me you'd never touched her.

676
00:30:57,720 --> 00:30:58,780
Just that one time.

677
00:30:59,310 --> 00:31:00,420
Please believe me.

678
00:31:00,550 --> 00:31:02,550
After leaving your place that time,

679
00:31:03,600 --> 00:31:05,230
I finally managed to do it.

680
00:31:21,960 --> 00:31:22,440
Rong.

681
00:31:24,550 --> 00:31:26,830
You really didn't say anything
to Zhang Yi'ang?

682
00:31:26,830 --> 00:31:28,760
I really didn't even get to see him.

683
00:31:31,000 --> 00:31:32,600
I'll trust you one last time.

684
00:31:34,990 --> 00:31:36,360
Is it really yours?

685
00:31:37,400 --> 00:31:38,160
Yes.

686
00:31:38,640 --> 00:31:39,670
It is mine!

687
00:31:39,830 --> 00:31:40,240
Well,

688
00:31:40,480 --> 00:31:42,640
shouldn't you at least
do the math on the dates?

689
00:31:42,640 --> 00:31:43,560
No need.

690
00:31:44,880 --> 00:31:45,720
It's Qi's,

691
00:31:45,880 --> 00:31:46,790
then it's mine!

692
00:31:49,510 --> 00:31:51,440
Are you insane?

693
00:31:51,460 --> 00:31:54,310
Your dying here
would still be an embarrassment to me.

694
00:31:54,310 --> 00:31:56,170
How could I have a friend like him?

695
00:31:58,160 --> 00:31:59,740
Ren, can I come up now?

696
00:31:59,790 --> 00:32:00,390
Ren!

697
00:32:00,480 --> 00:32:00,960
Qi,

698
00:32:01,400 --> 00:32:02,610
why did you come?

699
00:32:02,640 --> 00:32:04,110
I was worried about you!

700
00:32:04,260 --> 00:32:05,710
Be careful with our baby!

701
00:32:05,750 --> 00:32:07,550
I can't live without you!

702
00:32:25,180 --> 00:32:27,140
[Crime Scene Fingerprint Record Card]

703
00:32:25,880 --> 00:32:27,200
The fingerprints have been matched.

704
00:32:27,200 --> 00:32:27,790
These two

705
00:32:27,240 --> 00:32:27,990
[Fingerprint Comparison]

706
00:32:28,270 --> 00:32:29,480
are the suspects

707
00:32:29,480 --> 00:32:30,680
in the provincial capital explosion case.

708
00:32:30,680 --> 00:32:31,920
One is called Fang Chao,

709
00:32:31,920 --> 00:32:33,250
and the other is Liu Zhi.

710
00:32:35,830 --> 00:32:37,030
Let me add something.

711
00:32:37,240 --> 00:32:38,030
Because these two

712
00:32:38,030 --> 00:32:39,640
are skilled at disguising themselves,

713
00:32:39,640 --> 00:32:40,960
the Provincial Department's task force

714
00:32:40,960 --> 00:32:41,720
never managed to obtain

715
00:32:41,720 --> 00:32:42,780
their real photos.

716
00:32:43,310 --> 00:32:44,880
Li Qian found these,

717
00:32:45,270 --> 00:32:47,070
which allowed us
to confirm their identities.

718
00:32:47,070 --> 00:32:48,030
Catch these two men.

719
00:32:48,030 --> 00:32:48,880
See if we can uncover

720
00:32:48,880 --> 00:32:49,960
evidence against Zhou Rong from them.

721
00:32:49,960 --> 00:32:50,680
Once we have it,

722
00:32:50,680 --> 00:32:52,030
none of them will get away.

723
00:32:52,030 --> 00:32:53,070
Before noon tomorrow,

724
00:32:53,070 --> 00:32:54,070
we might be able to do it.

725
00:32:54,070 --> 00:32:54,470
Chief,

726
00:32:55,070 --> 00:32:55,670
thumbs up.

727
00:32:55,790 --> 00:32:56,110
No.

728
00:32:56,310 --> 00:32:57,770
The credit goes to Li Qian.

729
00:32:57,790 --> 00:32:58,990
Everyone, thumbs up!

730
00:33:01,590 --> 00:33:02,310
Chief Qi called for me.

731
00:33:02,310 --> 00:33:04,240
I need to go report to Director Gao.

732
00:33:05,480 --> 00:33:06,210
Chief Zhang!

733
00:33:07,070 --> 00:33:07,870
Two thumbs up!

734
00:33:08,030 --> 00:33:08,790
Chief Zhang!

735
00:33:08,830 --> 00:33:10,590
Thumbs up!

736
00:33:13,110 --> 00:33:14,270
Alright, get back to work.

737
00:33:14,270 --> 00:33:15,200
Get back to work.

738
00:33:15,440 --> 00:33:17,480
I'm going back to work, Captain Wang.

739
00:33:17,480 --> 00:33:17,940
I'm out.

740
00:33:22,480 --> 00:33:23,010
Xing?

741
00:33:23,030 --> 00:33:24,110
Xing? You're back.

742
00:33:25,810 --> 00:33:26,990
Song Xing, you're back.

743
00:33:26,990 --> 00:33:29,990
Song Xing, you're back.
What's with that expression?

744
00:33:32,430 --> 00:33:33,480
Song Xing, you're back!

745
00:33:33,480 --> 00:33:34,740
What's with that look?

746
00:33:36,830 --> 00:33:37,810
He's mad.

747
00:33:38,440 --> 00:33:40,640
Who wronged him? He looks so aggrieved.

748
00:33:46,160 --> 00:33:46,960
What's wrong?

749
00:33:51,980 --> 00:33:52,490
Laugh.

750
00:33:53,310 --> 00:33:54,440
Just keep laughing.

751
00:33:54,680 --> 00:33:55,680
Soon enough,

752
00:33:55,700 --> 00:33:56,270
you'll know

753
00:33:56,270 --> 00:33:57,160
who the biggest contributor

754
00:33:57,160 --> 00:33:58,180
to this case really is.

755
00:33:58,180 --> 00:33:59,130
Fine, it's you.

756
00:34:00,940 --> 00:34:01,760
No!

757
00:34:02,160 --> 00:34:03,400
It's the Chief and me!

758
00:34:04,310 --> 00:34:05,300
Yes.

759
00:34:05,440 --> 00:34:06,440
Yes.

760
00:34:07,440 --> 00:34:08,760
What do you even know?

761
00:34:09,710 --> 00:34:11,550
Today was a trap set by the Chief.

762
00:34:11,630 --> 00:34:12,280
He intentionally let

763
00:34:12,280 --> 00:34:13,590
those two suspects escape.

764
00:34:13,590 --> 00:34:15,520
It wasn't me who screwed things up!

765
00:34:16,880 --> 00:34:17,780
Yes, yes.

766
00:34:19,670 --> 00:34:20,600
I'm telling you,

767
00:34:20,670 --> 00:34:21,530
don't doubt me.

768
00:34:22,320 --> 00:34:23,320
Think carefully—

769
00:34:23,880 --> 00:34:25,150
haven't we been unable to find evidence

770
00:34:25,150 --> 00:34:27,080
against Zhou Rong this whole time?

771
00:34:27,510 --> 00:34:28,909
But in Zhou Rong's villa,

772
00:34:29,070 --> 00:34:29,710
Li Qian

773
00:34:30,070 --> 00:34:30,880
overheard those two

774
00:34:30,880 --> 00:34:33,190
planning to make a deal with Zhou Rong
over the phone.

775
00:34:33,190 --> 00:34:34,110
So if we catch them in the act

776
00:34:34,110 --> 00:34:35,280
when they make the deal,

777
00:34:35,280 --> 00:34:37,030
wouldn't that give us evidence?

778
00:34:37,030 --> 00:34:37,800
If today

779
00:34:37,840 --> 00:34:39,100
I had caught those two,

780
00:34:39,190 --> 00:34:39,760
how would they still be able to

781
00:34:39,760 --> 00:34:41,219
make a deal with Zhou Rong?

782
00:34:42,510 --> 00:34:43,370
Get it now?

783
00:34:44,110 --> 00:34:46,110
The Chief let them go on purpose!

784
00:34:55,320 --> 00:34:56,590
Is what you just said true,

785
00:34:56,590 --> 00:34:57,550
or are you talking nonsense?

786
00:34:57,550 --> 00:34:58,680
Of course it's true.

787
00:34:58,840 --> 00:35:01,040
The Chief explicitly hinted at it to me.

788
00:35:01,360 --> 00:35:02,160
Who else

789
00:35:02,480 --> 00:35:03,610
did you tell this to?

790
00:35:11,070 --> 00:35:11,870
What's wrong?

791
00:35:12,540 --> 00:35:13,870
Can you make it by tomorrow at noon?

792
00:35:12,580 --> 00:35:14,040
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

793
00:35:16,630 --> 00:35:18,710
As long as we can catch

794
00:35:18,920 --> 00:35:20,550
the suspects
we've already identified today,

795
00:35:20,550 --> 00:35:21,920
tomorrow should be no problem.

796
00:35:21,920 --> 00:35:22,320
Yes.

797
00:35:23,320 --> 00:35:23,880
But just in case

798
00:35:23,880 --> 00:35:24,630
we fail to catch Zhou Rong,

799
00:35:24,630 --> 00:35:25,890
please don't blame me.

800
00:35:26,440 --> 00:35:27,040
Work hard.

801
00:35:28,190 --> 00:35:29,320
Don't embarrass me.

802
00:35:30,880 --> 00:35:31,680
Director Gao.

803
00:35:31,760 --> 00:35:32,770
Yi'ang is now

804
00:35:32,800 --> 00:35:34,510
making his big move
after lying low for a while.

805
00:35:34,510 --> 00:35:36,170
He's really spread his wings.

806
00:35:36,880 --> 00:35:37,280
Director Gao,

807
00:35:36,990 --> 00:35:40,880
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

808
00:35:37,630 --> 00:35:38,630
please come over.

809
00:35:39,510 --> 00:35:40,240
Hold on a sec.

810
00:35:41,110 --> 00:35:41,640
Chief Qi.

811
00:35:44,440 --> 00:35:45,240
What's wrong?

812
00:35:46,590 --> 00:35:47,710
S-Something's wrong.

813
00:35:47,710 --> 00:35:49,670
Director Gao knew he was claiming
that Chief Zhang...

814
00:35:49,670 --> 00:35:50,470
Zhang Yi'ang.

815
00:35:52,510 --> 00:35:52,920
Here.

816
00:35:53,280 --> 00:35:54,360
Was it you who told Song Xing

817
00:35:54,360 --> 00:35:56,950
to deliberately let
Fang Chao and Liu Zhi escape?

818
00:35:56,950 --> 00:35:59,520
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

819
00:35:57,000 --> 00:35:57,840
What?

820
00:35:58,190 --> 00:35:59,790
Did you ask him to let them go?

821
00:36:04,030 --> 00:36:04,590
No.

822
00:36:04,840 --> 00:36:05,700
Still denying?

823
00:36:06,710 --> 00:36:08,440
Word has already reached
the Provincial Department,

824
00:36:08,440 --> 00:36:10,030
saying you privately told Song Xing

825
00:36:10,030 --> 00:36:10,880
that in order to catch Zhou Rong,

826
00:36:10,880 --> 00:36:13,410
you deliberately
let Fang Chao and Liu Zhi go.

827
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:14,760
No wonder you dared to promise

828
00:36:14,760 --> 00:36:15,400
that you would definitely

829
00:36:15,400 --> 00:36:16,730
catch him by tomorrow noon!

830
00:36:16,730 --> 00:36:18,350
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

831
00:36:16,920 --> 00:36:19,180
Turns out you resorted to dirty tactics.

832
00:36:19,320 --> 00:36:20,530
Director Gao, this matter...

833
00:36:20,530 --> 00:36:22,130
Chief Zhang, don't admit it.

834
00:36:22,320 --> 00:36:23,340
Just say there was no such thing.

835
00:36:23,340 --> 00:36:24,070
Chief Zhang.

836
00:36:24,150 --> 00:36:24,880
Chief Zhang.

837
00:36:25,150 --> 00:36:26,380
If you admit this,

838
00:36:26,440 --> 00:36:27,880
Director Gao will discipline you.

839
00:36:27,880 --> 00:36:29,070
If you say it was Song Xing's own doing,

840
00:36:29,070 --> 00:36:29,710
we'll handle him internally.

841
00:36:29,710 --> 00:36:30,690
That gives us more room to maneuver.

842
00:36:30,690 --> 00:36:32,320
Now is the critical moment
to solve the case.

843
00:36:32,320 --> 00:36:33,000
We must abandon the rook to save the king.

844
00:36:33,000 --> 00:36:34,070
Sacrifice the part to save the whole.

845
00:36:34,070 --> 00:36:34,800
Chief Zhang,

846
00:36:35,070 --> 00:36:35,960
I shouldn't have

847
00:36:35,960 --> 00:36:36,780
leaked your plan.

848
00:36:36,780 --> 00:36:37,850
Just sacrifice me.

849
00:36:57,440 --> 00:36:57,900
Well...

850
00:36:58,020 --> 00:36:59,030
We're in the middle of a meeting
with Director Gao!

851
00:36:59,030 --> 00:36:59,800
What are you doing?

852
00:36:59,800 --> 00:37:00,530
Get out. Out.

853
00:37:05,590 --> 00:37:06,150
Director Gao,

854
00:37:06,150 --> 00:37:06,880
sorry about that.

855
00:37:06,880 --> 00:37:08,000
The connection just dropped.

856
00:37:08,000 --> 00:37:08,730
Where is Zhang Yi'ang?

857
00:37:08,040 --> 00:37:08,920
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

858
00:37:09,630 --> 00:37:10,440
He stepped out.

859
00:37:10,440 --> 00:37:11,250
Get him back here!

860
00:37:10,490 --> 00:37:11,600
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

861
00:37:11,880 --> 00:37:12,320
Okay.

862
00:37:13,190 --> 00:37:13,710
Yi'ang?

863
00:37:14,510 --> 00:37:15,030
Yi'ang!

864
00:37:17,110 --> 00:37:17,570
Yi'ang.

865
00:37:18,030 --> 00:37:19,070
Pin it on me.

866
00:37:24,360 --> 00:37:25,160
Director Gao.

867
00:37:25,320 --> 00:37:25,920
Director Gao.

868
00:37:25,920 --> 00:37:26,520
He's here.

869
00:37:29,860 --> 00:37:35,370
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

870
00:37:30,000 --> 00:37:30,800
Zhang Yi'ang,

871
00:37:32,030 --> 00:37:33,190
did you instruct Song Xing

872
00:37:33,190 --> 00:37:34,590
to deliberately
let Fang Chao and Liu Zhi go?

873
00:37:34,590 --> 00:37:35,050
Tell me!

874
00:37:39,700 --> 00:37:40,620
Don't admit it.

875
00:37:41,110 --> 00:37:42,320
Director Gao,
the connection is a bit laggy...

876
00:37:42,320 --> 00:37:43,120
Director Gao!

877
00:37:45,360 --> 00:37:47,400
I am now the Deputy Chief
of the Sanjiangkou Public Security Bureau

878
00:37:47,400 --> 00:37:49,600
in charge of criminal investigations.

879
00:37:50,320 --> 00:37:52,580
This case falls under our jurisdiction.

880
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:54,240
If anything goes wrong, it's on me.

881
00:37:54,240 --> 00:37:55,990
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

882
00:37:55,880 --> 00:37:57,760
Everything we've done
is for the sake of solving the case.

883
00:37:57,760 --> 00:37:58,400
Now

884
00:37:59,110 --> 00:38:01,170
is not the time to pursue the details.

885
00:38:02,190 --> 00:38:02,990
Zhang Yi'ang,

886
00:38:04,000 --> 00:38:05,920
haven't seen you for a few days,
and you've grown.

887
00:38:05,610 --> 00:38:07,440
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

888
00:38:07,800 --> 00:38:08,670
Those are suspects

889
00:38:08,670 --> 00:38:09,800
of the provincial capital explosion case!

890
00:38:09,800 --> 00:38:10,920
How dare you!

891
00:38:11,550 --> 00:38:12,920
You have to risk something
to catch something.

892
00:38:11,620 --> 00:38:13,080
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

893
00:38:14,400 --> 00:38:15,480
Screwing things up

894
00:38:15,480 --> 00:38:16,880
is nothing new for you!

895
00:38:17,760 --> 00:38:18,880
If they get away,

896
00:38:18,920 --> 00:38:20,510
can you take responsibility for that?

897
00:38:20,510 --> 00:38:21,360
R-Responsibility...

898
00:38:21,360 --> 00:38:23,230
I'll bear it together with Yi'ang.

899
00:38:23,230 --> 00:38:25,150
I'm the head of the Sanjiangkou Bureau,

900
00:38:25,150 --> 00:38:26,230
the first person accountable.

901
00:38:26,230 --> 00:38:27,930
If you want to punish someone,
punish me first.

902
00:38:27,930 --> 00:38:30,580
[Police Internal Video Communication System]

903
00:38:29,300 --> 00:38:30,100
Director Gao,

904
00:38:30,550 --> 00:38:33,150
we're at a crucial stage
of the investigation.

905
00:38:33,230 --> 00:38:35,510
Just let Yi'ang handle things his way.

906
00:38:43,630 --> 00:38:45,560
I'll give you until noon tomorrow.

907
00:38:45,800 --> 00:38:47,730
If you haven't caught them by then,

908
00:38:47,760 --> 00:38:48,960
you'll answer for it.

909
00:38:57,770 --> 00:38:58,510
Thank you.

910
00:40:01,020 --> 00:40:01,750
Uncle Yifei,

911
00:40:02,510 --> 00:40:04,640
why hasn't Zhou Rong contacted us yet?

912
00:40:05,710 --> 00:40:06,650
Who do you think is

913
00:40:06,650 --> 00:40:07,980
more anxious, him or me?

914
00:40:10,030 --> 00:40:10,880
Z-Zhou Rong.

915
00:40:13,840 --> 00:40:14,610
Exactly.

916
00:40:18,550 --> 00:40:19,280
Uncle Yifei,

917
00:40:19,550 --> 00:40:20,610
when are we eating?

918
00:40:20,920 --> 00:40:21,800
Soon.

919
00:40:22,070 --> 00:40:22,460
Alright.

920
00:40:22,460 --> 00:40:23,550
You're as fat as a pig,

921
00:40:23,550 --> 00:40:24,550
and you're still thinking about food?

922
00:40:24,550 --> 00:40:25,080
Get lost!

923
00:40:27,880 --> 00:40:28,510
Zheng,

924
00:40:29,150 --> 00:40:31,080
I can see you're getting restless.

925
00:40:32,030 --> 00:40:33,190
Why don't you go for a run

926
00:40:33,190 --> 00:40:34,990
and buy me a bottle of fish sauce?

927
00:40:48,070 --> 00:40:48,550
Later,

928
00:40:48,630 --> 00:40:49,110
after we finish checking

929
00:40:49,110 --> 00:40:50,320
these few households,

930
00:40:50,320 --> 00:40:51,320
let's go check somewhere else.

931
00:40:51,320 --> 00:40:51,650
Okay.

932
00:40:52,960 --> 00:40:53,440
Sir,

933
00:40:54,110 --> 00:40:55,780
you just moved here, right?

934
00:40:56,320 --> 00:40:56,670
Yes.

935
00:40:57,800 --> 00:40:58,200
Hello.

936
00:40:58,230 --> 00:40:59,630
We're from the subdistrict office,

937
00:40:59,630 --> 00:41:01,280
conducting a census check.

938
00:41:01,310 --> 00:41:02,000
May I see

939
00:41:02,000 --> 00:41:02,730
your ID card?

940
00:41:02,800 --> 00:41:03,360
Sure.

941
00:41:09,550 --> 00:41:10,120
My ID card.

942
00:41:09,920 --> 00:41:10,690
[Name: Zhu Hao]

943
00:41:13,400 --> 00:41:15,070
Is it just you living here?

944
00:41:15,840 --> 00:41:16,950
We're in the transport business.

945
00:41:16,950 --> 00:41:18,800
There are a few other workers as well.

946
00:41:18,800 --> 00:41:19,400
Then please

947
00:41:19,400 --> 00:41:20,210
have them come out.

948
00:41:20,210 --> 00:41:21,440
We'll register everyone together.

949
00:41:21,440 --> 00:41:22,100
No problem.

950
00:41:22,940 --> 00:41:24,940
[Jiangping Community Resident Registration Form]
[Name: Zhu Hao]

951
00:41:23,320 --> 00:41:23,780
Chubby!

952
00:41:25,230 --> 00:41:26,110
Come out, all of you!

953
00:41:26,110 --> 00:41:26,970
Bring your IDs!

954
00:41:27,360 --> 00:41:28,560
Registration check!

955
00:41:30,440 --> 00:41:31,370
Stand properly!

956
00:41:38,490 --> 00:41:39,270
[Wanted]

957
00:41:39,270 --> 00:41:40,050
[Suspect Photo: Huo Zheng]

958
00:41:46,060 --> 00:41:46,450
[Wanted]

959
00:41:46,450 --> 00:41:46,730
[Suspect Photo: Fang Chao]

960
00:41:57,840 --> 00:41:58,480
[Wanted]

961
00:41:59,280 --> 00:41:59,380
[Wanted]

962
00:41:59,410 --> 00:42:00,060
[Suspect Photo: Xia Tinggang]

963
00:42:02,340 --> 00:42:03,160
Sir,

964
00:42:03,230 --> 00:42:04,960
that vehicle out front is yours, right?

965
00:42:04,960 --> 00:42:05,820
Yes, it's mine.

966
00:42:05,920 --> 00:42:07,320
Then, when you have time,

967
00:42:07,320 --> 00:42:08,710
bring your vehicle registration
and driver's license

968
00:42:08,710 --> 00:42:09,550
to our office.

969
00:42:09,580 --> 00:42:10,710
We'll issue you an entry-exit permit.

970
00:42:10,710 --> 00:42:11,070
Okay.

971
00:42:11,510 --> 00:42:12,440
Okay, thank you.

972
00:42:12,440 --> 00:42:13,650
Alright, we won't trouble you further.

973
00:42:13,650 --> 00:42:14,510
Okay. Alright.

974
00:42:16,710 --> 00:42:17,360
Sir!

975
00:42:17,920 --> 00:42:20,680
Well, you haven't told me

976
00:42:20,770 --> 00:42:22,170
how to get to your office.

977
00:42:23,280 --> 00:42:24,670
Building 27, ground floor.

978
00:42:24,670 --> 00:42:26,130
There's a sign by the door.

979
00:42:28,960 --> 00:42:30,690
Huo Zheng!
